Effects.raw_text: Deep relaxation and body sedation. Strong initial euphoria followed by heavy couch-lock effects. Best for nighttime use, pain relief, and stress management. Linalool and myrcene contribute to muscle relaxation while caryophyllene helps with anti-inflammatory effects.

Heavy-hitting cerebral euphoria followed by strong body relaxation. Initial uplifting effects due to limonene but transitions into full sedation as myrcene and caryophyllene take over. Best for nighttime use, stress relief, and pain management.

Balanced hybrid with a euphoric head rush followed by smooth body relaxation. Limonene provides an initial mood boost, while myrcene and caryophyllene promote deep relaxation. Best for evening use, stress relief, and mild pain management.

Relaxing and heavy-hitting with a slow-building sedative effect. Starts with a subtle head high from limonene and gradually transitions into a full-body melt. Best for evening relaxation, pain relief, and stress reduction.

Strong euphoric rush followed by deep body relaxation. High limonene provides an uplifting start, transitioning into full sedation due to myrcene and caryophyllene. Ideal for pain relief, stress management, and evening use.

Energetic and euphoric start with a citrusy flavor, transitioning into a relaxed yet clear-headed experience. Limonene delivers an initial uplift, while myrcene and caryophyllene keep the high balanced. Ideal for daytime use, mood enhancement, and mild pain relief.

Relaxing with a mild euphoric onset, leading into deep sedation. Caryophyllene provides stress relief, while limonene adds a light uplifting effect. Ideal for nighttime use, anxiety reduction, and pain management.
